		<div class="home-title">
			<h1>Flight Delay</h1>
		</div>

		<div class=form-field-home>
			<form method="GET" action="/traveler/<%=traveler._id%>/new">
				<div class="container">
					<p>Flying is stressful enough. Why let delayed or cancelled flights give you more? Check to see if your flight is eligible for reinsurance, and get what you deserve.</p>

					<p>*The third-party Flight Tracking API we use is currently deprecated, and can only retrieve flight information for past flights from Henri CoandÄƒ International Airport on Blue Air Airlines.*</p>
					<div class="flightInput">
						<div class="flightNum">Flight Number:</div>
						<div class="flightNumInput"><input type="number" name="number"></div>
						<div class="searchDiv">
							<button class="searchButton">Search</button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<span class="home-message"><%=message%></span>
				</div>
			</form>


		</div>
		
